y, reconsidering the criteria—hints should focus on PascalCase class names, @Annotation names, property names, and exception names rather than conceptual descriptions. So \"トリム要否設定\" doesn't fit these categories and shouldn't be reported as a missing hint.\n\nThe knowledge file checks out as clean overall. No critical issues, the omissions are acceptable, and the hints appropriately cover the key technical terms.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":20108,"cache_read_input_tokens":29807,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":20108,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4f7aabf5-ba7f-44ec-a890-2b2c5271381c","uuid":"5aca9708-9563-4ee7-88e2-d00cc81a52d3"}
